First, for the head of the pin, it’s a simple cylinder. The cylinder is 35 mm in diameter and 20mm thick. Then for the shaft of the pin, there’s another cylinder that’s 20mm in diameter and 60mm long. So the total length of the metal pin (head + shaft) is 80mm.
